title: Exki - Kleber
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Health food concept chain shop with many outlets in Paris. Sandwiches and salads. Ingredients are given, hot (including soups) and cold dishes. Uses some organic produce and fruit and veg. Comfortable place with Wi-Fi, near Arc de Triomphe.
